  name "Cli 0 3 84 Release Published"
  description "Given the extractor scaffold command is merged on main, when @topogram/cli 0.3.84 is prepared, published, smoke-tested, rolled to first-party consumers, and release evidence is refreshed, then strict release status is green for the CLI and first-party consumers."
